{"tid":1977804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"檢舉匪諜，人人有責","createTime":"2020-04-18T08:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T07:22:33.000Z","uid":91721,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb03d471962e605f4fd69879ec80a016e410fb26","tid":1977804,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:32:45.000Z","msg":"根據《兩岸人民關係條例》第33條規定，台灣地區人民、法人、團體或其他機構，不得擔任經行政院大陸委員會會商各該主管機關公告禁止之大陸地區黨務、軍事、行政或具政治性機關（構） 、團體之職務或為其成員。第90條規定，違反規定者，處新台幣10萬元以上50萬元以下罰鍰。<br />\n<br />\n相關機構包括：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mac.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=29B3D06675FAF607&amp;sms=2EB2D59F2BF0C2BE&amp;s=D7CDA689FDBCB368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mac.gov.tw%2FNews_Content.aspx%3Fn%3D29B3D06675FAF607%26sms%3D2EB2D59F2BF0C2BE%26s%3DD7CDA689FDBCB368&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppemWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=747add62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mac.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=29B3D06675FAF607&amp;sms=2EB2D59F2BF0C2BE&amp;s=D7CDA689FDBCB368</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你認識任何台灣人喺以上機構工作，請立即向中華民國大陸委員會報告</span></span><br />\n<br />\n聯絡資料：<br />\n大陸委員會政風室<br />\nE-mail：ethics@mac.gov.tw"},{"pid":"73dc2167df6f52f5deffc56d575b39c1233d9386","tid":1977804,"uid":235875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:33:53.000Z","msg":"實用，推"},{"pid":"f78d7e7ce85cbac5ec09abfaf9074c650114774e","tid":1977804,"uid":91721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:39:53.000Z","msg":"致品葱民国派手足🇹🇼：<br />\n<br />\n结束共产党于中国大陆的统治，以及迎回中国国民党，建立民主、正统的中华民国，是我等民国派的愿望。<br />\n<br />\n为此，即使身处沦陷区、为共匪工作，亦请不忘为中华民国付出。<br />\n<br />\n请立即寻找、调查不忠诚的中华民国国民，并通报中华民国大陆委员会，为中华民国尽忠！<br />\n<br />\n三民主義　吾黨所宗\t<br />\n以建民國　以進大同\t<br />\n咨爾多士　為民前鋒\t<br />\n夙夜匪懈　主義是從\t<br />\n矢勤矢勇　必信必忠"},{"pid":"1d10a02c3eca6884760e7631d52c761e6107c742","tid":1977804,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f78d7e7ce85cbac5ec09abfaf9074c650114774e","tid":1977804,"ui